":"Menos frecuente en AM vs jovenes","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Mandibula atrofica → Fx de angulo y cuerpo","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Riesgo lesion nervio alveolar inferior","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"58","parent":"53","text":"Fractura\\Ncondilar","guid":"Y2uRv6LZPWF1_AomF4_a4g","children":[{"id":"59","parent":"58","text":"Dolor ATM, limitacion apertura oral","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"58","text":"Malocclusion","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"61","parent":"31","text":"Fractura nasoetmoidal\\N(NOE)","guid":"tT1aquidHWNEu9TRKqXWUA","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Telecanto traumatico","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Fistula LCR → rinolicuorrea","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Clasificacion Markowitz I-II-III","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"0","text":"HEMOSENO","guid":"","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Definicion → acumulacion de sangre dentro del seno paranasal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Fisiopatologia","guid":"","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"Fractura de pared sinusal → laceracion mucosa → sangrado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"Sangre se acumula por gravedad en seno afectado","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"67","text":"Mas frecuente en SENO MAXILAR (por Fx piso orbitario o pared anterior)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"67","text":"Tambien en seno frontal y etmoidal","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"72","parent":"65","text":"Hallazgo\\Nradiologico","guid":"sVcEQa4DdXXm6yVMv7tNUg","children":[{"id":"73","parent":"72","text":"TC sin contraste → nivel hidroaereo o velamiento completo del seno","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"72","text":"Opacificacion unilateral del seno → SOSPECHAR Fx asociada","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"72","text":"Rx Waters → velamiento seno maxilar (baja sensibilidad)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"76","parent":"65","text":"Significado\\Nclinico","guid":"IZT7PeSLZqmI-H6j2sKvCQ","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"MARCADOR INDIRECTO de fractura de pared sinusal","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"Hemoseno aislado sin Fx visible → seguimiento","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"Hemoseno + fractura desplazada → evaluar cirugia","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"80","parent":"65","text":"Complicaciones\\Ndel hemoseno","guid":"tJboXODSgXl1PdzoVumk1w","children":[{"id":"81","parent":"80","text":"Sobreinfeccion → sinusitis aguda postraumática","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"82","parent":"80","text":"Mucocele tardio (semanas a meses)","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"80","text":"Fistula oroantral (si Fx alveolar asociada)","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"65","text":"Manejo","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"Conservador en mayoria → resolucion espontanea 2-4 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"ATB profilacticos →\\NCONTROVERSIAL","guid":"qx_B4CGG08djOaWtsN-HtQ","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Evidencia NO apoya curso corto ATB para prevenir sinusitis","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"Considerar si contaminacion, Fx expuesta o inmunosupresion","guid":"","children":[]}]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"Descongestionantes nasales y lavados salinos","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"84","text":"Seguimiento con TC control si no resuelve en 4-6 semanas","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"84","text":"Drenaje quirurgico solo si sinusitis refractaria o mucocele","guid":"","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"92","parent":"0","text":"Complicaciones\\NAsociadas","guid":"rVol-iXwzt_zjeLyurEmeA","children":[{"id":"93","parent":"92","text":"Lesiones concomitantes\\Nfrecuentes en AM","guid":"ojtH38zvyG8cM3KIwoGFVA","children